<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">40-70 ans</td>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Information, soutien psychologique</td>
<td class="border border-gray-300 px-4 py-2">Associations, centres sociaux</td>
</tr>
